node.title: Dionne Warwick Jumps Into Taylor Swift's 'All Too Well' Discourse With Funny Tweets
node.alt: Dionne Worwick added to the "All Too Well" conversation Monday when she sent out a pair of tweets referencing the "scarf" from the famous song. Taylor Swift attends the "All Too Well" New York Premiere on November 12 in New York City.
node.description: "If that young man has Taylor's scarf he should return it," Warwick tweeted about Swift's supposed "Easter egg."
node.content:
["Since the release of Taylor Swift's latest \"Taylor's Version\" album Red on November 12, it seems every corner of the internet is discussing the project.", "One of the most anticipated aspects of her recent release was the inclusion of a 10-minute version of the singer's highly regarded song All Too Well. The song, which was first released on the original album in 2012, was named the best song of the 2010s by Rolling Stone.", "Not only was there an addition of almost 5 minutes of music, the singer also released a short film to correspond with the longer version starring actors Dylan O'Brien and Sadie Sink. The song has long been understood to be about Jake Gyllenhaal who Swift is said to have dated in 2010 for about three months.", "", "
Dionne Worwick added to the \"All Too Well\" conversation Monday when she sent out a pair of tweets referencing the \"scarf\" from the famous song. Taylor Swift attends the \"All Too Well\" New York Premiere on November 12 in New York City.
", "Fans were quick to pick out many \"Easter eggs\" within the song and short film that further proved the theory about the song's inspiration.", "Another symbol fans have long clung to is the \"scarf.\" One of the first few lyrics in the song says:", "\"I, left my scarf there at your sister's house/And you've still got it in your drawer even now.\"", "And later in the song, the lyrics refer back to the same scarf saying, \"But you keep my old scarf from that very first week/'Cause it reminds you of innocence/ And it smells like me.\"", "Naturally, a red scarf made an appearance in the film.", "While everyone continues to dissect the song and all its hidden, or not so hidden, messages, another singer is chiming in with her two cents.", "Dionne Warwick has become quite the Twitter comedian, contributing to all kinds of conversations online. A Warwick character has even become a mainstay on Saturday Night Live\u2014with the real Warwick making a special appearance on the show earlier this month.", "On Monday, Warwick tweeted, \"If that young man has Taylor's scarf he should return it.\"", "It was followed by another tweet that read: \"It does not belong to you. Box it up and I will pay the cost of postage, Jake.\"", "Though in the 10 years since the pair's romance, Swift has never explicitly discussed the relationship.", "Her response? \"I haven't thought about their experience, to be honest.\""]
